This project has been created with the help of this blog.
https://dev.to/ivadyhabimana/how-to-create-a-react-app-without-using-create-react-app-a-step-by-step-guide-30nl

Helpful steps for beginners
---------------------------
npm -v
mkdir folder
cd /folder
npm init -y      
//package.json is created
npm install --save-dev @babel/core babel-loader @babel/cli @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react
//node_modules folder is created
npm install --save-dev webpack webpack-cli webpack-dev-server
npm install react react-dom


--------------------------------------------------
Note I can use either npm or yarn

npm install react react-dom
yarn add react react-dom
//Dev_Dependencies
npm install --save-dev @babel/preset-env react-hot-loader webpack webpack-cli webpack-dev-server @babel/core @babel/preset-react babel-loader
yarn add --save-dev react-hot-loader webpack webpack-cli webpack-dev-server @babel/core @babel/preset-react @babel/preset-env babel-loader
--------------------------------------------------
